<span id="freeTextContainer1160148568182780688">Really, really enjoyed this book. It&apos;s another self-pubbed book that I can&apos;t understand why it didn&apos;t find an agent or publishing home. Sighs...the biz. <br/><br/>I loved all the different supernatural characters being part of our good witch Ivy&apos;s life. I loved the opening with her needing a date for the dance and changing Spike from a lizard to a hot model. Lots of humor interspersed in the novel. <br/><br/>Great chemistry with Nick and Ivy. I was hoping she&apos;d get her act together to see how much he really cared f</span>
