      <span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_review_456858249'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it gr-button gr-button--small" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F10772961-the-book-of-lost-souls">Like</a></span>
